Embedded_text: Private jets are awful for the climate. It’s time to tax the rich who fly in them | Edward J Markey

Thank you, Senator Edward J. Markey, for meeting with our Massachusetts #StarsofLife. We appreciate your time, thought, and support. #EMS #SupportEMS #AlwaysOpen https://stars.ambulance.org/tag/2023+MA/

This week, U.S. Senator Edward J. Markey (D-MA) introduced a resolution calling for living wages, good benefits, and fair working conditions for all ESP who serve as the backbone of our schools. CAESS President Stacey Tayman spoke to what it means for ESPs to be heard.
